```plantuml
@startuml chrispiro_deploy_plotly_app_on_gcp

actor User
participant "GCP SDK" as gcp_sdk
participant "App Engine" as app_engine
participant "Cloud Build" as cloud_build
participant "Container Registry" as container_registry
participant "Dash App" as dash_app
participant "BigQuery" as bigquery
participant "Cloud Storage" as cloud_storage

User -> gcp_sdk: gcloud app deploy
activate gcp_sdk

gcp_sdk -> cloud_build: Submit build request
activate cloud_build

cloud_build -> container_registry: Pull base image
activate container_registry
container_registry --> cloud_build: Image pulled
deactivate container_registry

cloud_build -> cloud_build: Install dependencies\n(requirements.txt)
cloud_build -> cloud_build: Package application
cloud_build -> container_registry: Push built image
activate container_registry
container_registry --> cloud_build: Image pushed
deactivate container_registry

cloud_build --> gcp_sdk: Build complete
deactivate cloud_build

gcp_sdk -> app_engine: Deploy new version
activate app_engine
app_engine -> app_engine: Scale instances
app_engine --> gcp_sdk: Deployment complete
deactivate app_engine

gcp_sdk --> User: Deployment successful
deactivate gcp_sdk

User -> dash_app: Access application
activate dash_app
dash_app -> bigquery: Query data
activate bigquery
bigquery --> dash_app: Return data
deactivate bigquery

dash_app -> cloud_storage: Retrieve assets
activate cloud_storage
cloud_storage --> dash_app: Return files
deactivate cloud_storage

dash_app -> dash_app: Render visualizations
dash_app --> User: Display dashboard
deactivate dash_app

@enduml
```